    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This functor is used by <ref refid="classDali_1_1SignalDelegate" kindref="compound">SignalDelegate</ref> in order to callback to a non-static member function (after it has been converted to a <ref refid="classDali_1_1CallbackBase" kindref="compound">CallbackBase</ref>). The functor can be passed in to a ConnectSignal function of a <ref refid="classDali_1_1BaseHandle" kindref="compound">BaseHandle</ref> and call into an object&apos;s member function on despatch. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
